    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I'm not sure what to test other than checking that `Image` allows `format='bmp', embed=True`.\r\n\r\nI don't think this will actually make `Image` do what you want - you add support for putting bmp data in, but nothing ever takes it out of `Image`. Maybe the best option is to convert to png on demand, and only support embedding bmp if the tools we need to do the conversion are found. To be honest, I'm still not sure why anyone wants to embed bmp data anyway..."
