    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I think this PR is once again in a state that won't achieve anything; it lets you put bmp format data into `Image`, but nothing will actually get it out of there.\r\n\r\nNobody's ever made a persuasive case for embedding bmp images: they're not common nowadays, and can be losslessly converted to png (which we do support embedding). I'm going to close this for now. If anyone wants to make the case, please do so on #9456."
